      "role": "user",
      "content": "but that's the problem. focusing on \"small things\" or \"stabilizing\" just feels like more maintenance on a machine that's already dead. it's like i'm just patching holes in a sinking ship. no matter how much i stabilize, the loop just restarts. eventually you realize the only way to actually stop the cycle is to just... not be in it anymore.",
